summary: A small Way House for travelers on the road to rest.
descriptionHtml:
A small way house near Riverwood.

\"Take what you need, leave what the next person will need.\"

---------------------

Features:
Two beds!
Fireplace!
Near the road!
Storage!
Relative Safety!

---------------------

Things to come:
Chests randomize inventory to simulate other travelers.
Random NPCs inside, USUALLY friendly
Possible upstairs storage

----------------------

Incompatibilities:
I\'m pretty sure there are none, but if it would be anything, it would be race height modifiers. The ceiling is relatively low and a very tall High Elf or Nord MAY not fit. Please alert me if this is so.
author: Ogachi
